  m_text: "Name: RAGHAV                   Room No:  268\t\t     IP No:  398/17                       
    AGE:2 YERS\t    Sex:M \t                            MRD No: PICU0023/24\r\nADDRESS:13,BARNABY
    ROAD,KILPAUK,CHENNAI-10\r\n\r\nWeight: 5 KG\r\nAdmitted On:29.11.2023\r\nPROVISINAL
    DIAGNOSIS: Acute renal failure/Post streptococcal glomerulonephritis\r\n\r\n\rBLOOD
    GROUP: O + VE\r\nDischarged on:\r\n\r\nHISTORY OF PRESENTING ILLNESS: 2 years
    old ragav was admitted in the hospital with h/o \r\npassing blood in urine and 
    puffiness of face for the past 2 days . H/o fever with pharyngitis 2 \r\nweeks
    back and was treated accordingly. Mother notices hematuria , facial puffiness
    and anuria since 12 hrs .\r\n\r\nGENERAL EXAMINATION: \r\nO/E - Normotheric \r\n\r\npedal
    edema +, \r\npallor ++\r\nPuffiness of face +\r\nSKIN/MUCOUS MEMBRANE: DRY\r\n\r\nCvs
    - s1s2 +, no murmur \r\nRs- B\\L crepts +\r\nP/A- mild distension + \r\nCns-
    Nfnd\r\n\r\nVitals \r\nTemp- 98 \r\nHr-120/min\r\nSpo2 -92 %\r\nBp- 100/70 mmhg
    \r\nRR-62"
